NK039(ti)002:1: // dpal ldan lha mo'i gsol mchod phrin las kyi gzhungs bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)002:2: na mo gu ruh dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs //
NK039(ti)002:4: bdud mo srog gi gzer chung gi //
NK039(ti)002:5: bsnyen bsgrub las kyi rim pa bstan //
NK039(ti)002:6: de la lha mo bsgrub pa'i thabs 'di la //
NK039(ti)002:11: de la dang po sngon 'gro'i rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:12: gnas ni dur khrod shing gcig gam /
NK039(ti)002:14: byang shar du lta ba'i brag phug gam lha 'dre drag po gnas pa'i sar bsgrub par bya ste /
NK039(ti)002:15: rnal 'byor pa dbang thob cing dam tshig dang ldan
NK039(ti)002:16: pas gnyen po lha yi bsnyen pa them pa'i rnal
NK039(ti)002:17: 'byor pas gang du bya bas gnas der dkyil 'khor
NK039(ti)002:18: mda' gang gru bzhi pa'i steng du /
NK039(ti)002:19: phung shul la sogs pa'i sa la gru gsum nag po bang rim gsum pa /
NK039(ti)002:20: rgyar gru gang zabs su khru phyed pa dug khrag gi nag por byug la /
NK039(ti)002:21: gru gsum du mchog phur gsum log gsum la gtsang brgyad srin mo'i 'gros su sgrel la /
NK039(ti)002:22: de rnams kyi kha sha dum re 'og tu ling ga re bzhag /
NK039(ti)002:23: de'i phyi rim zlum skor gsum byas la /
NK039(ti)002:27: de'i nang du ling ga gzhug pa sogs 'og tu 'byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK039(ti)002:28: de nas bstan rdzas kyi rims pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:29: gtor ma 'bru sna tshogs las byas pa'i phye ma
NK039(ti)002:30: rak+ta chang phud bdud rtsi sbrus pa'i bshos bu nag
NK039(ti)002:31: po zur gsum pa gcig snod gang yang rung ba'i
NK039(ti)002:32: nang du bzhag / de'i mthar mi dbang gi sha /
NK039(ti)002:34: khrim 'chal sha la sogs pa'i sha sna tshogs kyi bskor /
NK039(ti)002:35: mda' bya rgod ma gcig la skyes dar ma drir
NK039(ti)002:36: shi ba'i tsit+ta'i rtsa sbub dbu mar 'bod rbad bsad
NK039(ti)002:37: gsum gyi sngags dri khrag dang tshal gyi bris la
NK039(ti)002:38: gzhug / dar nag gi dril la mad'i mgul du btag go //
NK039(ti)002:39: gzhan yang tsaka li dang ne'u le'i rkyal bu'i nang du mi dbang gi dbang po lnga dang /
NK039(ti)002:40: bye ru la sogs rin po che sna tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)002:42: rma bya'i sgro dar sna tshogs bong bu'i snying /
NK039(ti)002:43: shing lo rlung khyer byang sems dkar dmar /
NK039(ti)002:45: mi bsod pa'i mtshon cha la ral gri sor brgyad pa yu bar /
NK039(ti)002:47: de rnams mda' yi mgul du btag brten gtor khar gzugs /
NK039(ti)002:48: de'i steng du dar nag gi gdug phub /
NK039(ti)002:49: gzhan yang mda' bya rgod ma'i mgul du bud med chur shi ba'i srin lag dang /
NK039(ti)002:50: ba dan rtse gsum rnams btag la rang gi g.yas
NK039(ti)002:51: su bzhag de rnams brten pa'i rdzas kyi rim pa'o
NK039(ti)002:52: // de nas dngos gzhi'i rim pa la /
NK039(ti)002:53: thog mar mtshams dang bsrung bas 'khor lo dang skyabs sems yan lag bdun pa rnams byas la /
NK039(ti)002:54: rang nyid phyag rdor ram yi dam gang rung ba bzlas pa'i bar rdzogs par bya'o //
NK039(ti)002:55: de nas lha bsgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:56: bdag cag gi phyi nang gi bar chad zhi zhing
NK039(ti)002:57: bstan la sdang ba'i dgra bo rnams bsgral nas sangs
NK039(ti)002:58: rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par bya bas
NK039(ti)002:59: don du lha mo bsnyen cing bsgrub par bya bsnyams
NK039(ti)002:60: du bsam la / sems bskyed de lha mo'i mngon rtogs bsgom pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:61: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+ha wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK039(ti)002:62: skad cig gis mi dmigs pa'i ngang las mdun du
NK039(ti)002:63: b+h+r+aumsmug nag 'bar ba gcig yongs su gyur pa las
NK039(ti)002:64: thod pa skom rlon gyis gzhal yas khang gru bzhi
NK039(ti)002:65: go bzhi pa / zhing chen gyi ka gdung /
NK039(ti)002:71: nyi zla'i skar khung byas pa /
NK039(ti)002:72: steng na zhing chen gyi rgyal mtshan gtsug pa /
NK039(ti)002:73: gtog la zhing gi gdug 'khor ba /
NK039(ti)002:75: blos rdzogs tshad gcig bskyed do //
NK039(ti)002:76: de'i phyi rol du bskal pa'i me ri 'bar bas gur khang /
NK039(ti)002:77: de'i phyi rol du bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshub ma'i gur khang 'khor ba /
NK039(ti)002:78: 'og gi sa gzhi la mi ro dang rta ro gcal du bkram pa /
NK039(ti)002:79: mi khrag dang rta khrag gi mtsho 'khyil ba /
NK039(ti)002:80: de nas gang du g+har+b+ha pa h+aumhzhesa brjod pa'i /
NK039(ti)002:81: gzhal yas khang de'i dbus su tihls sprul pas bong du dmar ga rlung gi gshog pa can /
NK039(ti)002:82: thod skom 'bar bas sga bstad pa /
NK039(ti)002:83: srin po'i yan 'gal la snga ru byas pa srin mo'i man 'gal la phyi ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)002:84: gong thag glo smed sbrul la byas pa /
NK039(ti)002:85: ru sbal nag po'i phog gu btab pa /
NK039(ti)002:86: snga shad g.yas na bdud kyis khram bam /
NK039(ti)002:87: snga shad g.yon na tshon gyi gru gu /
NK039(ti)002:88: phyi shad g.yas na byang dmar gyi bam ro /
NK039(ti)002:89: phyi shad g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa 'gel ba /
NK039(ti)002:90: mi mgo'i thod sdom byas pa snyan gnyis na mi lag gnyis 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)002:91: mjug ma na mig gcig yod pa /
NK039(ti)002:92: b+aa su ta yi zhag pa'i mthur ching byas pa /
NK039(ti)002:93: de'i sga gong du zhing chen bsnol bas gdan gyi steng du /
NK039(ti)002:95: de'i steng du rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+yohnaga mo gcig 'phros /
NK039(ti)002:97: bstan la sdang ba'i dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK039(ti)002:98: tshur 'dus b+h+yo la thimah de yongs su gyur pa
NK039(ti)002:99: las dpal ldan lha mo sku mdog mthing nag la
NK039(ti)002:100: rngam pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum dmar la
NK039(ti)002:101: zlum pa / me stag gi tsha tsha 'phro ba /
NK039(ti)002:102: phyag g.yas pas ral gri sdig pa can nam mkha' la phyar ba /
NK039(ti)002:103: g.yon pas b+han+d+ha lcang lo can khrag gi bkang ba thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)002:104: mchan na ne le'i rkyal pa thog pas kha nas
NK039(ti)002:105: rin po che 'phyur ba'i tshul gyi chun bu 'phyang
NK039(ti)002:106: ba / ral pa dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa'i
NK039(ti)002:107: skra mtshams su thod pa skom po lngas dbu brgyan
NK039(ti)002:108: ba / dang / rin po che'i rtse phran lnga'i brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)002:109: spyi bo nas zla ba tshes pa /
NK039(ti)002:110: lte ba nas nyi ma shar ba /
NK039(ti)002:111: spyi gtsug na rma bya'i rgyal mtshan gtsug pa /
NK039(ti)002:112: snyan shal g.yas gong na seng ge 'gying ba /
NK039(ti)002:113: g.yon na sbrul nag gi gdengs ka 'phyo ba /
NK039(ti)002:114: snyan gnyis na gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK039(ti)002:115: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK039(ti)002:116: glang chen gyi ko rlon sku stod la mnab pa /
NK039(ti)002:117: stag lpags gis sham thabs dang /
NK039(ti)002:118: mi rtsid kyi re lde'i sku smad dkris pa /
NK039(ti)002:119: thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal byas pa /
NK039(ti)002:120: rus pa dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)002:121: sku dang yan lag thams cad sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)002:122: de'i thugs kar ramhls nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyis steng
NK039(ti)002:123: du b+h+yohnaga mo gcig la sngags kyis g.yon du 'khor
NK039(ti)002:124: bar bsam / b+h+yohde las b+h+yohnaga mo 'bum 'phros pas
NK039(ti)002:125: 'khor bdud mo bye ba 'bum gyi tshogs dang bcas
NK039(ti)002:126: pa thams cad sku mdog nag mo ral pa sngo
NK039(ti)002:128: g.yas pa rnams kyi gri gug /
NK039(ti)002:129: g.yon pa rnams kyi thod khrag thog pa /
NK039(ti)002:130: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa sngo dmar 'chang ba /
NK039(ti)002:131: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi sku la mnab pa /
NK039(ti)002:133: 'khor bdud mo'i tshogs kyi gtso mo'i bka' nyan cing las byed pa'i tshur gyi bskor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)002:134: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:135: srin lag gi g.yab dar thog la /
NK039(ti)002:136: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK039(ti)002:138: thugs kar h'u sngon po bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i
NK039(ti)002:139: h'u sngon po de las 'od zer lcags kyu lta
NK039(ti)002:140: bu 'phros pas / ri rab kyi rtse mo byang
NK039(ti)002:141: shar gyi mtshams nas dpal ldan lha mo bzhugs pa'i
NK039(ti)002:142: thugs ka'i b+h+yohl phog pas sngon gyi thugs dam rjes
NK039(ti)002:143: su dran nas 'khor dang bcas pa skad cig gis
NK039(ti)002:145: b+h+yoh dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK039(ti)002:146: tshur gshegs tshur byon dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)002:147: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:148: rnal 'byor bdag gi gdongs te bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)002:149: nyi ma byang shar pha gi na //
NK039(ti)002:150: yongs 'dus shing gi rtsa ba na //
NK039(ti)002:151: matshohmu le mthing gi nang shed na //
NK039(ti)002:152: mthing shun sngon po'i gur khang na //
NK039(ti)002:153: thod pa dgu brtsegs gzhal yas na //
NK039(ti)002:154: bswe yi sku mkhar gru bzhi'i nang //
NK039(ti)002:155: rin chen sna tshogs pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)002:156: mi ro rta ro gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)002:157: mi khrag rta khrag 'dam rdzab ldang //
NK039(ti)002:158: de na ma gcig lha mo bzhugs //
NK039(ti)002:159: lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:160: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)002:161: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)002:162: chibs su bong bu dmar ga bcibs //
NK039(ti)002:163: khal du lcags kyi dra ba mig dgu 'gel //
NK039(ti)002:164: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa thog /
NK039(ti)002:165: g.yas na ral gri sdig pa can //
NK039(ti)002:166: g.yon na sdug pas thod khrag thog /
NK039(ti)002:167: stong gsum kun gyi byos blug mkhan //
NK039(ti)002:168: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:169: dam tshig dbang gi spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)002:170: dam la ma 'da' da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)002:171: ma gcig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:172: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum dang bcas //
NK039(ti)002:173: rnal 'byor bdag gi gdong ste bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)002:174: ma mchis ma thog myur du byon //
NK039(ti)002:175: ma cig lha mo nag mo khyod //
NK039(ti)002:176: sngon tshe phyag na rdo rje la //
NK039(ti)002:177: rang rtag srog gis snying po phul //
NK039(ti)002:178: bos nas 'ong bar khas blangs bzhin //
NK039(ti)002:179: khas blang dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)002:180: rnal 'byor bdag gi khyod bskul na //
NK039(ti)002:181: dam tshig dbang gi da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)002:182: thugs dam dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:183: ma gcig lha mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)002:184: na chung mtshan ldan chur shi yi //
NK039(ti)002:185: srin lag g.yab mos spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)002:186: mi dbang smin pas sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)002:187: dam rdzas 'di la myur du byon //
NK039(ti)002:188: e +aahr li ma h+aa ka li re ma ti
NK039(ti)002:189: sa ma ya dza dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes spyan
NK039(ti)002:190: drangs so // b+h+yoh ma gcig dpal ldan re ma ti phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum phrag rnams //
NK039(ti)002:191: mi ro gshibs pas gdan mchog dang //
NK039(ti)002:192: srid pa'i bong bu'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:193: ma h+aa ka li re ma tihs ma y+aa tish+tha lhan /
NK039(ti)002:195: b+h+yoh ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:196: nag mo chen mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)002:197: pho nya bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK039(ti)002:198: bdag gi dad pa'i phyag bagyi'o //
NK039(ti)002:199: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti a ti p+au ho /
NK039(ti)002:201: de nas dam sre ba 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)002:203: rdo rje dri chu bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK039(ti)002:204: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK039(ti)002:205: dam tshig dbang gi khrag chen po //
NK039(ti)002:206: bsre bas mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK039(ti)002:207: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)002:208: khyod dang bdag nyid dam basre'o //
NK039(ti)002:209: rtag tu dam la ma 'da' cig /
NK039(ti)002:210: dam las 'das na bsregs par byed //
NK039(ti)002:211: ma h+aa ku ku sa ma ya pany+tsa a mri ta la kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)002:213: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:214: b+h+yo ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:215: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum sde la //
NK039(ti)002:216: bu yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:217: rgya mtsho 'bab chu chu mig rdzings //
NK039(ti)002:219: ma yi sku la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)002:220: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)002:221: dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)002:222: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti ar+g+ham a h'u //
NK039(ti)002:223: chu skyes thangs skyes me tog dang //
NK039(ti)002:224: dbang po lnga yi me tog 'di //
NK039(ti)002:225: ma yi dbu la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa ka li re ma ti push+pe +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)002:226: ga bur gla rtsi ku kul dang //
NK039(ti)002:227: sha chen spos kyi dud pa 'di //
NK039(ti)002:228: ma yi shang la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa ka li re ma ti d+hup+pe +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)002:229: nyi zla glog dang gsal bas sgron //
NK039(ti)002:230: zhun chen mdangs kyi mar me 'di //
NK039(ti)002:231: ma yi spyan la thugs mchog dam pa dngos grub
NK039(ti)002:232: dam pa ma h+aa ka li re ma ti a
NK039(ti)002:234: khrag chen dug dang sbyar ba yi //
NK039(ti)002:236: ma yi thugs la thugs mchog dngos grub dam pa ma h+aa ka li re ma ti g+han+d+he +aahh+aum //
NK039(ti)002:237: phye ma lnga yi bshos bu dang //
NK039(ti)002:238: nal sha yon tan lnga ldan 'di //
NK039(ti)002:239: ma yi ljag la thugs mchog dngos grub dam ma
NK039(ti)002:240: h+aa ka li re ma ti ne wi te a
NK039(ti)002:241: h'u // pi wam gling bu mkhar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)002:242: man 'gal cha lang rkang gi dung //
NK039(ti)002:243: ma yi snyan la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa ka li re ma ti shab+ta a h'u /
NK039(ti)002:245: b+h+yoh rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)002:246: bum dang ril dang phye tshal dang //
NK039(ti)002:247: nang rol glo snying mkhal mar bcas //
NK039(ti)002:248: sha dang rus pa rkang tshil rnams //
NK039(ti)002:250: bstan pa bsrungs phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:251: ma ta ma mam sa la kh+aa hi //
NK039(ti)002:252: ma h+aa tak+ta ma h+aa tsit+ta la ma h+aa ba
NK039(ti)002:253: su ta ma h+aa ko ro tsa na ma h+aa
NK039(ti)002:254: ki ni ri ti la kh+aa hi //
NK039(ti)002:256: b+h+yoh ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)002:257: thugs dam dbang gi snying khrag dmar la rol //
NK039(ti)002:258: ma cig khrag 'thung dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)002:259: dam rdzas rmad du byung bas dmar chen bzhes //
NK039(ti)002:260: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi //
NK039(ti)002:261: ces pa'i rak+ta sbreng la 'bul lo //
NK039(ti)002:262: b+h+yoh sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:263: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)002:264: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:265: bdud rtsi sman gyis mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:266: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)002:267: zhes a mri ta la 'bul lo //
NK039(ti)002:268: b+h+yoh ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor bcas la //
NK039(ti)002:269: yang cig mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:270: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)002:271: 'chi ka'i mtshal tig dmar po dang //
NK039(ti)002:272: shing lo rlung khyer sar ma lhung //
NK039(ti)002:273: 'bras bu smin pa'i shing tog dang //
NK039(ti)002:274: na chung mo yi byung zad khrag /
NK039(ti)002:275: ma nyams byang sems dkar dmar dang //
NK039(ti)002:276: dri rgod snying dang dbang po lnga //
NK039(ti)002:277: bong bu'i snying dang khram 'chal sha /
NK039(ti)002:278: rnam lnga bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'di //
NK039(ti)002:280: bstan pa bsrungs phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:281: ces brten pa'i dam rdzas kyi mchod pa 'bul lo //
NK039(ti)002:282: de nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:283: h'u b+h+yoh ma cig chen mo 'khor bcas rnams //
NK039(ti)002:284: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)002:285: ma yi bu la dngos grub rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)002:286: ye shes gsang ba'i dngos grub 'dod khams 'dul ba'i
NK039(ti)002:287: 'jig rten dbang bsgyur ye shes lnga yi tshe bsod
NK039(ti)002:288: rgyas pa'i bdud rtsi sman gyi grub chen brgyad kyi
NK039(ti)002:289: phrin las rnam bzhi'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK039(ti)002:290: rtsal du gsol // sh+ri de wi ma h+aa ka li re ma ti ka ya sid+d+hi /
NK039(ti)002:291: wak+ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'uh sarba sid+d+hi h+r+aih zhes dngos grub blang ngo //
NK039(ti)002:292: de nas gdung shugs drag pos bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:293: b+h+yoh bskal pa me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)002:294: ma cig lha mo nag mo glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)002:295: pho nya bdud kyi bu mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)002:296: ma cig 'khor bcas btse bas bdag la dgongs //
NK039(ti)002:297: bdag nyid mi mkhas rmongs pa'i dbang gyur te //
NK039(ti)002:298: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)002:299: dam tshig nyams chag 'gal 'khrul gyur pa dang //
NK039(ti)002:300: ting 'dzin mi gsal ra ris khal khol dang //
NK039(ti)002:301: sngags dang phyag rgya dra chags zur nyams dang //
NK039(ti)002:302: nyams pa can gyi gribs kyi phog pa dang //
NK039(ti)002:303: phud nyams lhag mar gyur pa thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)002:304: dam rdzas mchod rdzas dus su ma 'tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)002:305: dpon g.yog mched lcam thugs dad 'gal ba dang //
NK039(ti)002:306: khyad par ma gcig dpal ldan lha mo yi //
NK039(ti)002:307: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)002:308: dam tshig nyams chag 'gal 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)002:309: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams la bshags //
NK039(ti)002:310: rab tu bshags so tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)002:312: de nas bstod pa bya ba ni 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)002:313: b+h+yoh bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)002:314: rlung nag dgu klong 'khrig pa'i pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)002:315: ma cig lha mo 'dod khams gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)002:316: nag mo za byed 'jig pa'i cha lugs can //
NK039(ti)002:317: mthing nag mi bsrun khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)002:318: mahkhyoda kyi sku mdog nag mor ston //
NK039(ti)002:319: don dam dbyings nas bskyed pa med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:320: ral pa g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:321: yum gyi mkha' la sprul pa'i 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:322: ral pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:323: thugs rjes sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:324: ral pa spyi bo'i gtsug tu 'khyil ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:325: thugs dam dgongs spyod gcig tu 'khyil pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:326: thod skam phreng bas dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:327: thugs rjes sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:328: rma bya'i rgyal mtshan dbu la bcug pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:329: phrin las rnam bzhi so sor mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:330: snyan cha g.yas na seng ge 'gying ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:331: dman mo thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:332: snyan g.yon sbrul nag gdeng ka 'phyo ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:333: zhe sdang ma spangs dbyings su dag pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:334: snyan cha gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:335: sangs rgyas kun la bsnyen bskur mdzad //
NK039(ti)002:336: spyan rtsa dmar po phyogs bcur gzigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:337: rnal 'byor srid gsum bya ra mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:338: shang nas nad kyi rlangs pa 'thul ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:339: sdang dgra la nad yams 'bebs pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:340: zhal gyi hom kheng drag po gdengs pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:341: dam rdzas gang yin zhal du gsol ba'i rno sdug mche ba zur gsum gtsigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:342: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i sha la rol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:343: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la mnabs pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:344: chos nyid yang dag don dang ldan pa yi //
NK039(ti)002:345: sku bstod glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:346: theg pa mchog gi don dang ldan /
NK039(ti)002:347: snam byed re lde nag pos dkris pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:348: 'jig rten 'di na che btsun ldan spyi bo'i gtsug na zla rgyas gsal ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:349: ma rig mun pa dbyings su dag pa'i lte ba'i dbus na nyi ma shar ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:350: srid pa'i rgyal mo gting nas bskom //
NK039(ti)002:351: stag gi lpags pas sham thabs byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:352: drag po'i cha lugs mngon du gyur pa'i phyag g.yas gdug pa'i ral gri phyar ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:353: dgra bgegs skye rgyud rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:354: phyag g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar chen bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:355: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal khrag ltar 'thung ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:356: mchan na ne'u le'u rkyal pa thog pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:357: bsgrub pa po la dngos grub ster ba'i zhabs la dbang gi lcags sgrog sgrog pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:358: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i phyir phyogs dril gyi pha la bcibs pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:359: log par lta ba'i dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i srin po'i ya 'gal snga ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:360: srin yul lang ga p+au ri bsgrod pa'i srin mo'i ma mgal phyi ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:361: srin khams ma lus dbang du bsdud pa'i gong thag glo smed sbrul la byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:362: zhe sdang gdug pa can rnams 'dul ba'i rus sbal nag po'i phog gus btab pa ni //
NK039(ti)002:363: klu bdud ma rung dam la 'dog pa'i snga shad bdud kyi khram bam bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:364: dam nyams dgra bo khram la 'debs pa phyi shad nad kyi rkyal ba bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:365: dam nyams dgra la nad yams 'bebs pa'i rtag /
NK039(ti)002:366: don dam bcud kyi rtags su zhag gi zo ris brgyan //
NK039(ti)002:367: thugs rjes chags pas rtags su rak+ta'i thig le'i brgyan //
NK039(ti)002:368: 'dul phyed phrin las rtags su thal bas tshom bu byug /
NK039(ti)002:369: ma mo 'bum phrag 'khor gyis bskor ba ni //
NK039(ti)002:370: stong gsum khyab par phrin las mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)002:371: b+h+yoh ma cig kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skoms //
NK039(ti)002:372: lag na rdo rje 'phen pas ri rab sil bur bsnyil //
NK039(ti)002:373: lha mo khyed la bdag gi btsun par bstod //
NK039(ti)002:374: b+h+yoh dpal ldan lha mo mthu chen khyod //
NK039(ti)002:375: chos skyongs rgyal mo mi zad ma //
NK039(ti)002:376: gsang ba'i dbyings phyug rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)002:377: bstan pa bsrungs mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:378: bstan pa rgyas mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:379: dngos grub ster mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:380: phrin las bsgrub mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:381: dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:383: de nas bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:384: rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka'i h'u gis mthar
NK039(ti)002:385: bskor du yi dam gyi sngags kyi g.yas su bskor
NK039(ti)002:386: ba de'i mthar lha mo'i sngags kyi bskor bar bsam
NK039(ti)002:387: / lha mo'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK039(ti)002:388: steng du b+h+yohls sngags kyi g.yon du bskor bar dmigs
NK039(ti)002:390: bdag gis thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pa'i lha
NK039(ti)002:391: mo'i zhal du zhugs thugs ka'i sngags phreng la phog
NK039(ti)002:392: / de las 'od zer sngags kyi phreng ba srog gi snying po yar zhal nas phyung /
NK039(ti)002:393: bdag gi zhal du zhugs thugs ka'i sngags phreng las g.yas bskor du bskor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)002:394: de las 'od zer 'phros rtsa dbu ma'i nang du mar zhugs gsang ba'i rdo rje nas byung /
NK039(ti)002:395: ma mo'i pad mar zhugs pa'i mchod pa sna tshogs
NK039(ti)002:396: kyis mchod nas mnyes shing tshims nas mthu dang nus
NK039(ti)002:398: thugs ka nas zhal nas tshur byung ba dag gi
NK039(ti)002:399: zhal du zhugs shing dngos grub sna tshogs ster bsam
NK039(ti)002:400: la / 'gal me'i 'khor lo bzhin du 'phreng ma chad par bsnyen pa gang rung bzlas so //
NK039(ti)002:401: thun 'jog dus su rang gi thugs ka'i h'u gi mthar 'khor bar bsam la nyer bsdu sogs bya'o //
NK039(ti)002:402: ma mo srog gi las brgyad dang /
NK039(ti)002:403: 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyi dmigs pa dang snga ni zur du bskol ba las shes so //
NK039(ti)002:404: de nas ci tsam bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK039(ti)002:405: sh+ri de wi sa p+aa ri wa ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK039(ti)002:406: shab+ta'i bar gyi mchod cing slar yang gtor ma la 'gugs gzhug byin rlabs byas te /
NK039(ti)002:409: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti sa pa ri
NK039(ti)002:410: wa ra i dam ba lan+tim kha kha kh+aa hi
NK039(ti)002:411: kh+aa hi / zhes pa lan gsum mam bdun gyi 'phul la /
NK039(ti)002:413: mchod do dpal ldan nag mo //
NK039(ti)002:414: ma rig pa rang byung gi rgyal mo dus bzhi'i lha mo'i sku la brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)002:415: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam /
NK039(ti)002:416: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma 'khor mkha' 'gro 'bum sde'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK039(ti)002:417: dam pa ye shes kyi chos skyong bsrung ma'i tshogs rnams la /
NK039(ti)002:418: gtor ma ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po 'di 'bul lo //
NK039(ti)002:420: bzhes nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung /
NK039(ti)002:423: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)002:424: dpal dang grags pa spel cig /
NK039(ti)002:425: tshe dang dbang thang bskyed cig /
NK039(ti)002:426: skye bo sdang byed kyi dgra sod cig /
NK039(ti)002:427: 'byung po gnod byed kyi bgegs thul cig /
NK039(ti)002:428: lha 'dre bar chad kyi rkyen bzlog cig /
NK039(ti)002:430: bar du gcod pa'i gnod byed thams cad thal ba rdul phran bzhin du brlag par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)002:432: de nas bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:433: b+h+yo dpal gyi srung ma khams gsum gtso mo khyod //
NK039(ti)002:434: bong bu rta mchog dpag tshad brgyad khri rgyug /
NK039(ti)002:435: re lde'i smad g.yog sbrul gyi sham thabs can //
NK039(ti)002:436: 'bar ba'i dbang rtag phyag na ral gri bsnams //
NK039(ti)002:437: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i ne'u le zhags pa g.yon //
NK039(ti)002:438: lte ba nyi shar gtsug tu zla rgyas gsal //
NK039(ti)002:439: nag mo khrag 'thung dbyings kyi dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)002:440: ma cig 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)002:441: dpal ldan re ma ti la bdag gis bstod //
NK039(ti)002:442: dam rdzas brgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)002:443: rnal 'byor bdag dang bdag gis 'khor rnams la //
NK039(ti)002:444: bdud dang dgra bgegs thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK039(ti)002:445: mi mthun gnod pa'i phyogs dang bral ba dang //
NK039(ti)002:446: dpal dang 'byor ba tshe dang gzi mdangs dang //
NK039(ti)002:447: 'khor dang longs spyod grags pa rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)002:448: bka' dang bstan pa bstan 'dzin kun bsrungs shig /
NK039(ti)002:449: bsdu na de tsam dang rgyas par mos na /
NK039(ti)002:450: b+h+yoh 'phrul gyi pho brang thod pa'i lding khang na //
NK039(ti)002:451: dpal ldan lha mo khrag 'thung re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:452: srin po nag po'i chung ma ral pa can //
NK039(ti)002:453: ya mtshan rmad byung lha mo khro rgyal gtso //
NK039(ti)002:454: zhal gdengs mche gtsigs drag pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK039(ti)002:455: rngams pa'i tshul gyis dmar chen khrag la rol //
NK039(ti)002:456: kha 'bar chen mo srog gi bshan pa mo //
NK039(ti)002:457: sku ni nag mo 'bum gyi dbus na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)002:458: skye ba rnam bzhi sgrol bas gang chen mo //
NK039(ti)002:459: khyod ni srid pa gsum gyi bskur bar 'os //
NK039(ti)002:460: tshangs pa'i rgyal pos rma bya'i rgyal mtshan phul //
NK039(ti)002:461: bdud kyi rgyal po'i khram bam nag pa phul //
NK039(ti)002:462: 'chi bdag rgyal po'i phyag mtshan ral gri phul //
NK039(ti)002:463: dur khrod ma mo'i b+han+da lcang lo phul //
NK039(ti)002:464: gnod sbyin rgyal po'i ne'u le rkyal pa phul //
NK039(ti)002:465: klu'i rgyal po'i sbrul nag gdengs ka phul //
NK039(ti)002:466: khyab 'jug chen po'i nyi ma zla ba phul //
NK039(ti)002:467: rnam thos sras kyi seng ge'i snyan cha phul //
NK039(ti)002:468: thogs chen rgyal po'i glang chen ko rlon phul //
NK039(ti)002:469: ma bdud rgyal mo'i re lde'i sham thabs phul //
NK039(ti)002:470: ma mo rnams kyi nad kyi rkyal pa phul //
NK039(ti)002:471: klu mo rnams kyi 'phrul gyi me long phul //
NK039(ti)002:472: sman mo rnams kyi mtshon gyi gru gu phul //
NK039(ti)002:473: sha za'i rgyal po'i thod pa'i phreng ba phul //
NK039(ti)002:474: lha phran rnams kyi gser gyi dril bu phul //
NK039(ti)002:475: sa bdag rgyal po'i rus sbal pho dgu phul //
NK039(ti)002:476: btsan gyi rgyal po'i shwa d+he'u dkar nag phul //
NK039(ti)002:477: srin po'i rgyal po'i lcags sgrog 'bar ba phul //
NK039(ti)002:478: rnal 'byor bdag gi bdud rtsi gtor ma phul //
NK039(ti)002:479: rak+ta dmar gyi ar+g+ham bsgrengs tsam na //
NK039(ti)002:480: ma la bus 'bod gdungs sems ma chung bar //
NK039(ti)002:481: smug nag 'jig pas rgyal mo'i skur bzhengs la //
NK039(ti)002:482: lcags kyu 'dra bas sder mo'i gtor ma longs //
NK039(ti)002:483: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i zhal gdongs la //
NK039(ti)002:484: za byed rno gdug 'bar ba'i mche bas gsol //
NK039(ti)002:485: le brgan khrag 'thung 'bar bas ljags rkyang la //
NK039(ti)002:486: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pas mgul du bstim //
NK039(ti)002:487: slob dpon pad ma 'byung gnas kyi mdzad pa'o //
NK039(ti)002:488: b+h+yo lha la dbang bsgyur lha mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)002:489: dbang phyug sras mo dkar mo dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)002:490: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)002:491: lha mo dpal 'bar ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:492: klu la dbang bsgyur klu mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)002:493: gtsug na rin chen bu mo yid 'ong ma //
NK039(ti)002:494: rol pa'i mtsho bdun gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)002:495: klu mo dpal 'bar ma la gnod sbyin dbang bsgyur gnod sbyin dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)002:496: gang ba bzang po'i bu mo shang dkar ti //
NK039(ti)002:497: nags tshal dra ba can gyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)002:498: gnod sbyin re ma ti la bdud la dbang bsgyur bdud mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)002:499: re ldem go nyag bu mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:500: bdud mkhar rtse dgu'i gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)002:501: bdud mo re ma ti la sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs bar zhal bzhes pas //
NK039(ti)002:502: chos nyid don rtogs 'phag ma re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:503: sa brgyad gnon pa'i sems ma re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:504: lha mo mthu chen khyod la dkon mchog mthu chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:505: rnal 'byor dgra 'dul khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:506: khyod kyi dngos grub ma lus bdag la dgongs //
NK039(ti)002:507: dam rdzas brgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)002:508: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)002:509: de nas yang dus bzhi'i bstod pa ni /
NK039(ti)002:510: b+h+yoh ma bcos chos sku bde ba chen po la //
NK039(ti)002:511: srid dang zhi bar mi gnas mnyam pa nyid //
NK039(ti)002:512: yon tan phrin las mtshan pas skur ston pas //
NK039(ti)002:513: dpal dang ldan pa'i lha mo khyod la 'dud //
NK039(ti)002:514: sku yi dkyil 'khor chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam //
NK039(ti)002:515: mya ngan mi 'da' mthun par snang ba nyid //
NK039(ti)002:516: mdzes pa'i brgyad ldan ma gcig re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:517: 'gro ba'i gnyen cig ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)002:518: chos sku mkha' ltar rtog pa'i shes rab la //
NK039(ti)002:519: thugs rjes rmad du byung ba'i thabs tshul gyis //
NK039(ti)002:520: ma rung gdug pa can rnams tshar gcod dang //
NK039(ti)002:521: mi bsnyil thugs dam can la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)002:522: dman pa mi 'dor rtags su bong bu bcibs //
NK039(ti)002:523: lha yi lha gyur lha min skrag mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)002:524: rdzu 'phrul shugs 'chang stong gsum khyab par nyul //
NK039(ti)002:525: bstan pa gnyen mdzad ma la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)002:526: dam rdzas brgyan pa'i gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)002:527: rnal 'byor bdag dang bdag gi 'khor rnams la //
NK039(ti)002:528: bdud dang dgra bgegs thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK039(ti)002:529: mi mthun gnod pa'i phyogs dang bral ba dang //
NK039(ti)002:530: dpal dang 'byor pa tshe dang gzi mdangs dang //
NK039(ti)002:531: 'khor dang longs spyod grags pa rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)002:532: bka' dang bstan pa bstan 'dzin kun srungs shig /
NK039(ti)002:533: khyung po rnal 'byor bas bstod pa rdzogs so //
NK039(ti)002:534: b+h+yoh gru gsum mthing nag zhal gyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)002:535: dur khrod mtha' mdzad dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)002:536: 'das dang ma byon kun la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)002:537: stong gsum 'jig rten kun gyi mdangs 'phrog ma //
NK039(ti)002:538: kun la dbang bsgyur 'khor lo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:539: bsam pa'i don 'grub nor bu rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:540: mi 'bral gzugs mdzes btsun mo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:541: bla med grogs tshol blon po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:542: theg pa'i mchog ldan glang po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:543: sa bcu sgrol mdzad rta mchog rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:544: 'jig rten mgon skyabs dmag dpon rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)002:545: mah'ajiga rten mgon po ltar ni bsod nams che //
NK039(ti)002:546: lha dbang brgya byin ltar ni longs spyod che //
NK039(ti)002:547: u ma de ba ltar ni cho rigs btsun //
NK039(ti)002:548: u dum wa ra ltar ni skye ba kun //
NK039(ti)002:549: me tog pad ma ltar ni lta bas mdzes //
NK039(ti)002:550: phyag na rdo rje ltar ni mthu stobs che //
NK039(ti)002:551: gcan gzan seng ge ltar ni dpa' bardzi che //
NK039(ti)002:552: nam mkha'i lha phran ltar ni sku 'khrus gsol //
NK039(ti)002:553: nor bu rin chen ltar ni gtsug tu khur //
NK039(ti)002:554: 'dzam gling rgyal po ltar ni bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)002:556: de nas bskang ba bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)002:557: b+h+yoh yongs 'dus shing sogs bskang ba rgyas pa'am /
NK039(ti)002:559: b+h+yoh ma cig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:560: sring cig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:561: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam cig ma //
NK039(ti)002:562: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)002:563: thugs dam bskang phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:564: nyams chag sel phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:565: phrin las bsgrub phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)002:566: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)002:567: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:568: zhing chen g.yab mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)002:569: brten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:570: mi dbang snying gi thugs rang bzhin gnas nas spyan
NK039(ti)002:571: 'dren mi rkang gling bu'i dam tshig gnyen po bsre
NK039(ti)002:572: ba'i phyir // bdud rtsi sman gyi /
NK039(ti)002:573: 'dod khams gtso mo yin rma bya'i rgyal mtshan ljags kyi dbang po tshim bya'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:574: sha chen dud pas mgrin pa'i gsang gnas sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)002:575: dmar chen rak+tasa nyams chag ma lus gso ba'i bya nag lug nag g.yag nag gi //
NK039(ti)002:576: dkar mo 'bum sde'i ser mo 'bum dmar mo 'bum
NK039(ti)002:577: ljang mo 'bum smug mo 'bum mthing nag 'bum ma
NK039(ti)002:578: yam rgyal mo'i bod khams brten ma'i 'dzam gling skyongs
NK039(ti)002:580: mahkhyoda kyang dam la ma 'da' cig /
NK039(ti)002:582: gal te dam las 'da' gyur na //
NK039(ti)002:583: srog gi snying po me 'bar nas //
NK039(ti)002:584: rang srog rang gis gcod par byed //
NK039(ti)002:585: de bas dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)002:586: thugs dam gnyen po 'di bskang bas //
NK039(ti)002:587: nyams chag gyur na bzod par gsol //
